  "prompt": "Who are some of the best lawyers in India?",
  "response": "India has a number of highly regarded lawyers and legal professionals across various fields of law. Some of the most notable lawyers in India include:\n\n1. **Fali S. Nariman** - A senior advocate known for his expertise in constitutional law and arbitration.\n2. **Harish Salve** - A prominent lawyer who has represented high-profile clients in various cases, including constitutional and commercial matters.\n3. **Kapil Sibal** - A former Union Minister and senior advocate known for his work in constitutional law and human rights.\n4. **Mukul Rohatgi** - Former Attorney General of India and a well-known advocate with expertise in constitutional and commercial law.\n5. **Indira Jaising** - A leading advocate known for her work in human rights law and women's rights.\n6. **Gopal Subramanium** - A former Solicitor General of India and a respected figure in constitutional and civil law.\n7. **Soli Sorabjee** - A former Attorney General of India and a prominent constitutional lawyer.\n8. **Sidharth Luthra** - A well-known criminal lawyer and advocate with significant experience in high-profile cases.\n\nThese lawyers have made significant contributions to the legal field in India and are often sought after for their expertise and experience in various legal matters.",
